'''地中海森林、疏林和灌叢'''（{{lang-en|'''Mediterranean forests, woodlands, and scrub'''}}）是屬於[[地中海型氣候|地中海型氣候]]的[[生物群系|生態群系]]，在此區域中，氣候特徵為夏季乾燥炎熱，冬季多雨涼爽。<ref name=wwf>{{cite web |url=http://www.panda.org/about_our_earth/ecoregions/about/habitat_types/selecting_terrestrial_ecoregions/habitat12.cfm |title=Mediterranean Forests, Woodlands, and Scrub Ecoregions |publisher=WWF |accessdate=2014-05-29 |archive-date=2011-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110401124536/http://wwf.panda.org/about_our_earth/ecoregions/about/habitat_types/selecting_terrestrial_ecoregions/habitat12.cfm |dead-url=yes }} (included verbatim material: licensed under [http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/ CC-BY-SA-3.0] {{Wayback|url=http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/ |date=20110223182903 }})</ref>

[[File:Mediterranean_forests_1.JPG|thumb]][[上加利利|上加利利]]的地中海森林]]

此生態群系均出現於世界五大地中海型氣候地区中，如下：<ref name="wwf" />
*[[地中海盆地|地中海盆地]]
*[[智利|智利]]{{link-en|馬托拉爾|Chilean Matorral}}
*{{link-en|加利福尼亞叢林|California chaparral and woodlands}}，位於[[加州|加州]]與[[下加利福尼亞半島|下加利福尼亞半島]]一帶
*{{link-en|西南澳|Southwest Australia|澳洲西南部}}
*[[南非|南非]][[開普省|開普省]]至[[西開普省|西開普省]]一帶

